@startuml anemic-architecture
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
title Anemic Domain Model — Architecture

package "Primary Adapter" <<Rectangle>> #E8F5E9 {
    [PortfolioRestController] as ctrl
}

package "Application Layer" <<Rectangle>> #E3F2FD {
    [PortfolioStockOperationsService] as svc
    note bottom of svc
      **Fat service — all business logic here:**
      • Inline FIFO loop with settlement check
      • Inline reservation check
      • Fee calculation and balance update
      • 70+ lines of business logic
    end note
}

package "Domain Model (Data Holders)" <<Rectangle>> #FFF3E0 {
    [Portfolio] as portfolio
    [Holding] as holding
    [Lot] as lot
    [SellResult] as result

    note bottom of portfolio
      sellWithSettlement():
        profit = proceeds − costBasis
        **(forgets fee)**
    end note

    note bottom of lot
      isAvailableForSale():
        isSettled(asOf)
        **(forgets !reserved)**
    end note
}

package "Secondary Adapters" <<Rectangle>> #FCE4EC {
    [JpaPortfolioRepository] as repo
    [FinhubStockPriceAdapter] as price
}

ctrl --> svc : uses port
svc --> portfolio : reads data
svc --> holding : reads lots
svc --> lot : inspects fields
svc --> result : creates
svc --> repo : saves/loads
svc --> price : fetches price

note right of svc
  **Two sell paths exist:**
  1. sellStockWithSettlement()
     → inline logic (CORRECT)
  2. sellStockWithSettlementAggregate()
     → delegates to domain (FLAWED)
end note

@enduml
